						               													<description>Veggie Battle is a hidden goal, tile drafting and placement game  for 2-4 players.  You play the role of one of several neighbors working in shared community gardens, scheming against each other  to win the coveted &amp;quot;Gardener of the Year&amp;quot; award.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player receives four Goals for the game, two of which are shared while the other two remain hidden.  Players also receive three Tool cards that allow them to take actions that are otherwise outside of normal gardening etiquette.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The gardens are represented by four 3x3 grids.  Players take turns drafting tiles representing one of seven different veggies and placing them in an unoccupied slot in any garden.  Once all gardens are completely planted, players assign one goal to each garden and calculate their harvest to determine who scored the veggie victory.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;quot;--description from the designer&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
